short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Track your job applications in the browser.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Job Application Tracker is a utility chrome plugin that allows the users to keep a tab on their job applications, helping them Add, edit and schedule and delete a job application right from their browser.
